<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمْ يَظْهَرُوا}</span> ... لَا عِلْمَ لَهُمْ بِأُمُورِ العَوْرَاتِ، وَلَيْسَ فِيهِمْ شَهْوَةٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا يُخْفِينَ مِن زِينَتِهِنَّ}</span> ... كَالخَلَاخِلِ الَّتي تُلْبَسُ فِي الأَرْجُلِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَنكِحُوا}</span> ... زَوِّجُوا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْأَيَامَى}</span> ... مَنْ لَا زَوْجَ لَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عِبَادِكُمْ}</span> ... عَبِيدِكُمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَإِمَائِكُمْ}</span> ... جَوَارِيكُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَبْتَغُونَ}</span> ... يَطْلُبُونَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْكِتَابَ}</span> ... المُكَاتَبَةَ، بِأَنْ يَشْتَرُوا أَنْفُسَهُمْ مِنْ أَسْيَادِهِمْ بِمَالٍ مُقَسَّطٍ يُؤَدُّونَهُ إِلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَيْرًا}</span> ... رَشَدًا وَقُدْرَةً عَلَى الكَسْبِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَيَاتِكُمْ}</span> ... جَوَارِيكُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْبِغَاءِ}</span> ... الزِّنَى.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَحَصُّنًا}</span> ... تَعَفُّفًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُورُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> هُوَ نُورٌ، وَكِتَابُهُ نُورٌ، وَبِهِ اسْتَنَارَتِ السَّمَوَاتُ وَالأَرْضُ، يُدَبِّرُ الأَمْرَ فِيهِمَا، وَيَهْدِي أَهْلَهُمَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَمِشْكَاةٍ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هِيَ:</span> الكُوَّةُ فِي الحَائِطِ غَيْرُ النَّافِذَةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>